cquarie Bank in Hong Kong. After leaving Macquarie in 2009 he spent 3 years setting up the equity desks at Chinese brokerages before moving to Indonesia fulltime as partner at Elite Havens Lombok in 2013. Chris set up NTB Capital later in 2013 to pursue private equity-type returns.  Chris has known Stewart for 8 years, purchased his first Lombok property in January 2013 and brings to the team a wealth of knowledge in structuring deals, sales and capital raising.'),(499,71,'_content_9_grid_item_0_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(500,71,'content_9_grid_item_0_avatar','69'),(501,71,'_content_9_grid_item_0_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(502,71,'content_9_grid_item_1_name','Stewart Strong'),(503,71,'_content_9_grid_item_1_name','field_561553c81174e'),(504,71,'content_9_grid_item_1_title','Founding Partner'),(505,71,'_content_9_grid_item_1_title','field_5615541711750'),(506,71,'content_9_grid_item_1_bio','Stewart is a former equity broker at Instinet in Hong Kong and CLSA in Jakarta. He left CLSA in 2012 to move \r\n\r\ndown fulltime and focus on his property interests in Lombok. Upon buying his first property in 2008 to build \r\n\r\na resort (Avantara), he instead opted to sub-divide part of it instead and made a significant return over 24 \r\n\r\nmonths. Holding onto most of the property, he then started a property brokerage business (Avantara Land \r\n\r\nConsulting) that has grown into Elite Havens Lombok with 26 fulltime employees, 2 offices and 1 satellite \r\n\r\noffice in Bali.'),(507,71,'_content_9_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(508,71,'content_9_grid_item_1_avatar','70'),(509,71,'_content_9_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(510,71,'content_9_grid_item_2_name','David Mulligan'),(511,71,'_content_9_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(512,71,'content_9_grid_item_2_title','Director - General Manager'),(513,71,'_content_9_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(514,71,'content_9_grid_item_2_bio','David is a former commercial real estate age