me','field_561553c81174e'),(874,77,'content_10_grid_item_2_title','Director - General Manager'),(875,77,'_content_10_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(876,77,'content_10_grid_item_2_bio','David is a former commercial real estate agent operating in Sydney for almost a decade. During this time, he\r\n\r\nwas a REINSW finalist in line for the Excellence in Commercial Sales and Leasing award and was a member of \r\n\r\nthe Property Council of Australia. David also worked as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a \r\n\r\nmajor Australian and US surfboard brand. David brings with him experience in both small and large business \r\n\r\nas well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably; management, project \r\n\r\ndevelopment, marketing and sales.'),(877,77,'_content_10_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(878,77,'content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','70'),(879,77,'_content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(880,77,'content_10_grid_item_3_name','Simon Barnes'),(881,77,'_content_10_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(882,77,'content_10_grid_item_3_title','Director'),(883,77,'_content_10_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(884,77,'content_10_grid_item_3_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(885,77,'_content_10_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(886,77,'content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','70'),(887,77,'_content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(888,77,'content_10_grid_item_4_name','Dane Crookham'),(889,77,'_conte