vatar','field_5615543511751'),(2080,87,'content_10_grid_item_1_name','Stewart Strong'),(2081,87,'_content_10_grid_item_1_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2082,87,'content_10_grid_item_1_title','Founding Partner'),(2083,87,'_content_10_grid_item_1_title','field_5615541711750'),(2084,87,'content_10_grid_item_1_bio','Stewart is a former equity broker at Instinet in Hong Kong and CLSA in Jakarta. He left CLSA in 2012 to move \r\n\r\ndown fulltime and focus on his property interests in Lombok. Upon buying his first property in 2008 to build \r\n\r\na resort (Avantara), he instead opted to sub-divide part of it instead and made a significant return over 24 \r\n\r\nmonths. Holding onto most of the property, he then started a property brokerage business (Avantara Land \r\n\r\nConsulting) that has grown into Elite Havens Lombok with 26 fulltime employees, 2 offices and 1 satellite \r\n\r\noffice in Bali.'),(2085,87,'_content_10_grid_item_1_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2086,87,'content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','70'),(2087,87,'_content_10_grid_item_1_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2088,87,'content_10_grid_item_2_name','David Mulligan'),(2089,87,'_content_10_grid_item_2_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2090,87,'content_10_grid_item_2_title','Director - General Manager'),(2091,87,'_content_10_grid_item_2_title','field_5615541711750'),(2092,87,'content_10_grid_item_2_bio','David is a former commercial real estate agent operating in Sydney for almost a decade. During this time, he\r\n\r\nwas a REINSW finalist in line for the Excellence in Commercial Sales and Leasing award and was a member of \r\n\r\nthe Property Council of Australia. David also worked as the National Sales & Customer Service Manager for a \r\n\r\nmajor Australian and US surfboard brand. David brings with him experience in both small and large business \r\n\r\nas well as practical skills and knowledge in a variety of key areas, notably; management, project \r\n\r\ndevelopment, marketing and sales.'),(2093,87,'_content_10_grid_item_2_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2094,87,'content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','70'),(2095,87,'_content_10_grid_item_2_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2096,87,'content_10_grid_item_3_name','Simon Barnes'),(2097,87,'_content_10_grid_item_3_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2098,87,'content_10_grid_item_3_title','Director'),(2099,87,'_content_10_grid_item_3_title','field_5615541711750'),(2100,87,'content_10_grid_item_3_bio','Simon spent a total of 13 years in investment banking, including stints at JPMorgan, Merril Lynch and BNP \r\n\r\nParibas, working in a number of areas including Corporate Advisory, a Credit Derivs prop trading desk and \r\n\r\nHedge Fund Prime Brokerage. Simon made his first land purchase in Lombok in 2010 and a second larger \r\n\r\npurchase in 2012. He joined Stewart and Chris on the NTB Capital team as a director in 2014, adding \r\n\r\nspecialist experience in offshore fund documentation and due diligence.'),(2101,87,'_content_10_grid_item_3_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2102,87,'content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','70'),(2103,87,'_content_10_grid_item_3_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2104,87,'content_10_grid_item_4_name','Dane Crookham'),(2105,87,'_content_10_grid_item_4_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2106,87,'content_10_grid_item_4_title','Project Manager'),(2107,87,'_content_10_grid_item_4_title','field_5615541711750'),(2108,87,'content_10_grid_item_4_bio','Not Finished'),(2109,87,'_content_10_grid_item_4_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2110,87,'content_10_grid_item_4_avatar','70'),(2111,87,'_content_10_grid_item_4_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2112,87,'content_10_grid_item_5_name','Jasma Wadi'),(2113,87,'_content_10_grid_item_5_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2114,87,'content_10_grid_item_5_title','Serangan Headland Operations Manager'),(2115,87,'_content_10_grid_item_5_title','field_5615541711750'),(2116,87,'content_10_grid_item_5_bio','Jas has the biggest smile in Lombok and it is continuously affixed on his face, generating happy vibes \r\n\r\neverywhere he goes. Jas lives in Praya and is a vital link to the community surrounding our project at \r\n\r\nSerangan. His role is to facilitate harmonious relationships with the local community, hire and oversee local \r\n\r\nworkers and work with village chiefs (Kadus) and local government parties (Bupati), as well as major \r\n\r\ngovernment departments, such as; PU Department (roads), PLN (electricity), PDAM (water) and BPN (Land & \r\n\r\nTitles).'),(2117,87,'_content_10_grid_item_5_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2118,87,'content_10_grid_item_5_avatar','70'),(2119,87,'_content_10_grid_item_5_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2120,87,'content_10_grid_item_6_name','Kartini Lumban Raja'),(2121,87,'_content_10_grid_item_6_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2122,87,'content_10_grid_item_6_title','Office Manager and Bookkeeper Coordinator'),(2123,87,'_content_10_grid_item_6_title','field_5615541711750'),(2124,87,'content_10_grid_item_6_bio','Kartini is a rambunctious go-getter who will take on any project with gusto. She is a trusted and very vital \r\n\r\nmember of our team helping us negotiate the challenging hurdles of conducting business in Indonesia. Born \r\n\r\nin Sumatra and married to a local man from Gerupuk, she studied accounting at Universitas Advent \r\n\r\nIndonesia, Bandung and was previously working as the Country Director for Help Indonesia Foundation in \r\n\r\nJakarta.'),(2125,87,'_content_10_grid_item_6_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(2126,87,'content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','70'),(2127,87,'_content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(2128,87,'content_10_grid_item_7_name','Tamara Cox'),(2129,87,'_content_10_grid_item_7_name','field_561553c81174e'),(2130,87,'content_10_grid_item_7_title','Community Relations, Branding and Social Media Manager'),(2131,87,'_content_10_grid_item_7_title','field_5615541711750'),(2132,87,'content_10_grid_item_7_bio','Tamara has a history of community health care as a practicing podiatrist, specializing in Diabetes educa