oundation in \r\n\r\nJakarta.'),(4314,158,'_content_10_grid_item_6_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(4315,158,'content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','70'),(4316,158,'_content_10_grid_item_6_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(4317,158,'content_10_grid_item_7_name','Tamara Cox'),(4318,158,'_content_10_grid_item_7_name','field_561553c81174e'),(4319,158,'content_10_grid_item_7_title','Community Relations, Branding and Social Media Manager'),(4320,158,'_content_10_grid_item_7_title','field_5615541711750'),(4321,158,'content_10_grid_item_7_bio','Tamara has a history of community health care as a practicing podiatrist, specializing in Diabetes education.\r\n\r\nBorn and raised in Sydney’s North Shore with a strong background in health and fitness, her interests lie in \r\n\r\nhelping others. In particular she hopes to educate local communities regarding healthy living and \r\n\r\nenvironmental issues. Smart, logical, creative and caring she spearheads our CSR and PR efforts, linking us \r\n\r\nwith local charities. Responsible for our image and branding, Tamara managed the creation and continues to \r\n\r\nmaintain and update our website.'),(4322,158,'_content_10_grid_item_7_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(4323,158,'content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','70'),(4324,158,'_content_10_grid_item_7_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(4325,158,'content_10_grid_item_8_name','Maman'),(4326,158,'_content_10_grid_item_8_name','field_561553c81174e'),(4327,158,'content_10_grid_item_8_title','Contracts Administrator'),(4328,158,'_content_10_grid_item_8_title','field_5615541711750'),(4329,158,'content_10_grid_item_8_bio','Not Finished.'),(4330,158,'_content_10_grid_item_8_bio','field_561553c81174f'),(4331,158,'content_10_grid_item_8_avatar','70'),(4332,158,'_content_10_grid_item_8_avatar','field_5615543511751'),(4333,158,'content_10_grid_item','9'),(4334,158,'_content_10_grid_item','field_561553c81174d'),(4335,158,'content_11_title','Open Positions'),(4336,158,'_content_11_title','field_560da8ce2a001'),(4337,158,'c